# Hyperparameter Optimization

test_score = []
neighbors = range(1, 25)

for k in neighbors:
    model = KNeighborsClassifier(n_neighbors=k)
    model.fit(X_train, y_train)
    test_score.append(accuracy_score(y_test, model.predict(X_test)))
